## 🏗️ Project Structure

```
orchids-curecoders/
├── 📁 public/                    # Static assets
├── 📁 src/
│   ├── 📁 components/            # Reusable UI
│   │   ├── 📁 ui/                # shadcn/ui primitives
│   │   ├── 📁 agents/            # 🤖 Agent cards & runners
│   │   ├── 📁 reports/           # 📄 Report renderers
│   │   └── 📁 layout/            # Header, sidebar, shell
│   ├── 📁 routes/                # TanStack Start file-based routes
│   │   ├── __root.tsx            # Root shell
│   │   ├── index.tsx             # Master Agent Workspace
│   │   ├── architecture.tsx      # 🏗️ Architecture page
│   │   ├── samples.tsx           # 📊 Sample outputs
│   │   ├── apis.tsx              # 🔌 Mock API catalog
│   │   ├── queries.tsx           # 🔍 Instant queries
│   │   ├── journey.tsx           # 🚀 Product journey deck
│   │   └── reports.tsx           # 📄 PDF / Excel exports
│   ├── 📁 lib/                   # Server functions & utilities
│   ├── 📁 hooks/                 # Custom React hooks
│   └── 📁 styles.css             # Tailwind v4 design tokens
├── 📄 README.md
├── 📄 LICENSE
├── 📄 CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md
├── 📄 CONTRIBUTING.md
└── 📄 SECURITY.md
```

